snippet.textDisplay: So gracefully sung! Listening again & again. Expecting more Nazrul gitis from Coke studio bangla. We have not explored enough yet on Kazi Nazrul's musical excellence.

snippet.textDisplay: This has been on repeat in my playlist since it was released. It is a beautiful and soothing masterpiece. The emotion conveyed by Coke Studio Bangla in their interpretation of this poem by Nazrul is incredible. Ishaan's voice is particularly captivating and has a calming effect on me every time I listen to it. It is a wonderful and emotional tribute to the immortal creations of Kazi Nazrul Islam. Eid Mubarak!
